{"word":"κρέξ","slug":"κρέξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n59820\" key=\"kre/c\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κρέξ</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, gen. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κρεκός</foreign>, a long-legged bird, perh. <sense id=\"n59820.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">corn-crake, Rallus crex</tr_>, or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ruff, Machetes pugnax</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τούτους</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λίθους</foreign>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐτύκιζον αἱ κρέκες τοῖς ῥύγχεσιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1138\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Av.\">Av.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1138</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg030:695a:22\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PA\">PA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">695a22</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:4:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ NA\">NA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.5</biblScope> </bibl>; sacred to Athena, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2034.tlg003:3:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Porph.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Abst.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.5</biblScope> </bibl>; [<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=